{"tid":205501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行路撚]東涌行去將軍澳(live)","createTime":"2017-04-17T22:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T18:14:30.000Z","uid":35774,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34622635d4c07f51b40d80d52b94390e017b2154","tid":205501,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:41:54.000Z","msg":"今次大熱天時行路<br />\n主要我都係想練返行路嘅速度，同埋熱天之下做運動嘅耐力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講咁多，準備出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出發時間：18/04/2017 ~09:00<br />\n起點：東涌地鐵站<br />\n終點：康城地鐵站<br />\n<br />\n路線：<br />\n東涌至欣澳 約11公里<br />\n目標完成時間：1.75-2小時<br />\n<br />\n之後喺欣澳站搭地鐵往青衣，喺青衣站繼續行程<br />\n<br />\n青衣至將軍澳 約24公里<br />\n目標完成時間：4.5小時<br />\n<br />\n裝備方面就一切從簡<br />\n最主要都係帶多啲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n途中我會試下用戴開嘅fitbit手帶記錄低路線同步數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12099929f38250f9327e8232e6d9fe820cde6638","tid":205501,"uid":102661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:43:50.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n加油呀樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6c590d76cfbe2af39218c74987749bef2821d1","tid":205501,"uid":35774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:43:58.000Z","msg":"隔離post巴打嘅徒步環港<br />\n大家記得入去支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/204054/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/204054/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"a7e9e1616bd0b5d90b9fdef1d062133e0b3bd680","tid":205501,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:45:36.000Z","msg":"行路撚路過"},{"pid":"dc9f74cf2cab8f1d9f1a366fc2959c369d01667a","tid":205501,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:46:47.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"7f79bd2ad34e382671